Package: handyFunctions
Type: Package
Title: Useful functions for handfully manipulating and analyzing data with data.frame format
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hongfei Liu
Maintainer: Hongfei Liu <lhf563@126.com>
URL: https://github.com/LuffyLouis/handyFunctions
BugReports: https://github.com/LuffyLouis/handyFunctions/issues
Description: Some useful functions for simply manipulating and analyzing data with data.frame format.
    It mainly includes the following sections: 
    ReformatDataframe
        modifyColnames: modify the colnames of raw data.frame
        modifyColTypes: automatically recognize and change the data types of each col
        modifyRownames: modify the rownames of raw data.frame
        unifyDataframe: reformat dataframe with the above all modifiers simultaneously
        splitCol: return specific-indexed vector according to given delimitator/separator by splitting one col in data.frame
    InteractDataframe
        mergeCustom: merge two data.frame based on xcol and ycol
        matchIndex: return index of x data.frame with the given vector/list or ycol in data.frame (if set the accurate match or not)
    Post-VCF
        plotSNVdensity: Function of showing SNP density at chromosome level
